            "title": "IRON STORAGE DISEASE IN CAPTIVE EGYPTIAN FRUIT BATS (ROUSETTUS AEGYPTIACUS): RELATIONSHIP OF BLOOD IRON PARAMETERS TO HEPATIC IRON CONCENTRATIONS AND HEPATIC HISTOPATHOLOGY",
            "creators": [
