            "title": "Calcium as a limiting resource to insectivorous bats: can water holes provide a supplemental mineral source?",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Rick A.",
                    "lastName": "Adams"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
